<big><strong><center><font size="6.2">Keeping your PC updated</font></center></strong></big>
<br style = “line-height:150px;”>


<p><font size="4.5">
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft">Microsoft</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apple_Inc.">Apple</a> very often release updates regarding their operating system and a user is recommended to install these updates by the time they are available. These updates usually include fixes that improve the security of your system.
Windows users can install updates using a feature called <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4027667/windows-10-update">Windows Update</a> while on the other hand, Apple uses a feature called <a href="https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201541">Software Update</a>.
For more information on these kind of updates, i encourage you to visit these links for more tips on how to install these updates:

