<big><strong><center><font size="6.2">Importance of system updates</font></center></strong></big>


<p><font size="4.5">Software updates offer plenty of benefits. These might include repairing security holes that have been discovered and fixing or removing computer bugs. Updates can add new features to your devices and remove outdated ones. Moreover Software updates help protect your data from cybercriminals.Also, if your device gets infected by a virus, you
could pass it on to your friends, family, and business associates. That’s why  keeping your software and systems updated is necessary.
Last but not least, every user deserves the latest and greatest. Updates can also add new features and improve existing ones. Program performance will also be boosted.</font></p>


